name: Wendy William
description:
Happy Perky and Fun Loving…
Just a very Nice women and im looking for friends and see where life takes me… Im In the Here and Now and im excited about 2014, I ready to do Some dating and just experence life . share some good times with a very Special man. Could that be You.!!!!!! ~~~~~ I wont know inless you write me and let me know your interested…
Hi….Have been single for a while and its been all good but starting to miss the benefits that come with a relationship. I like to laugh & have fun. I just want to enjoy life & the only thing missing is that special man to spend it with.
Im wishing you Much happiness… and a sweet Spirit too LOVE ~~~~~~
